Welcome to the JackBot Website


 About


JackBot is a Discord Bot full of memes, quotes and many other things that are about or relevant to the YouTuber JackSucksAtLife. The original version of this bot was created on the 
22/04/2018
 by 
Cairo#4883
, But version 3.0.0 was created on the 
19/09/2018
.

docs.text:
Command Documentation


The command prefix is
 
jb!
 or 
@JackSucksAtBot#5488
 
you are able to change this using the
 
prefix
 
command.


 Help Commands




help
 - Displays the help screens main menu


system
 - Displays all of the system commands


memes
 - Displays all of the memey commands


videomemes
 - Displays all of the video meme commands


utilities
 - Displays all of the utility commands


ate
 - Dispalys all of the ate commands




 System Commands




info
 - Gives you information about the JackBot, the Developer and JackSucksAtLife


links
 - Provides links to the Website, Support Server and Bot Invite


support
 - Alias of 
links


website
 - Alias of 
links


invite
 - Alias of 
links
 


updatelogs
 - Links you to the updatelogs


version
 - Gives you the version the bot is currently running


ping
 - This response was decently quick, right?


bugs
 - Provides the link to report a bug


github
 - Provides the link to the bot's github


trello
 - Provides the link to the bot's trello


donate
 - Provides the link to donate


partner
 - Sends a list of partners


prefix
 - Allows you to change the prefix for your server




 Memey Commands




dead
 - The baby wipes flavour from the beanboozled challenge is disgusting.


vomit
 - The beanboozled flavour vomit is great!

 - Just me being immature as usual

 - I always kill pets on accident - it's not my fault

 - I had a massive brain fart here

 - insert clap here

 - OMG! OMG! I'm so excited!!

 - I said GET OUT!

 - I really like the tesco clubcard collection you got there

 - My room is a mess now, ugh.

 - It's normal to have a cleaver in your clothes, right?


kazoodrop
 - His behaviour was disgusting


smh
 - Jesus christ...


crotch
 - Hehehehhe - I'm just looking down

 - DIE YOU WORTHLESS ****


psychopath
 - Hehehehehe


weird
 - Just being a bit weird as usual

 - I have come to invade planet earth


shocked
 - OML!!!


uhh
 - Woops..


wtf
 - Let me reconsider some life choices


singing
 - Baby, baby, baby ooh


suited
 - Brother and sister moment, beautiful


please
 - Get some help

 - *insert facepalm here*

 - B!tch f●●● off


angelic
 - Hallelujah!


kazooholder
 - It's built in!


flamin
 - Damn it's hot


satan
 - *demonic voice activated*

 - Hmmm

 - sWirLY


overnight
 - overnight challenge anyone?

 - the kazoo possesses you

 - BOOM

 - *insertdroolemojihere*

 - It's official, the grave.

 - IM A MONSTER!


duet
 - oooowoahah 


broke
 - I'm soo poor ;-;


paidpromotion
 - oh no.. not jack too


nose
 - My nose on a [spoiler]


bloodyhell
 - Oh bloody hell




 Video Meme Commands


These commands are restricted to the Donator(s)

Become a donator by typing the command 
jb!donate




spin
 - You spin me right round..


scumbag
 - You lil' scumbag




 Utility Commands




weather <location>
 - Gives you information on the weather in that location 




 Active Testing Enviroment


These commands are restricted to the BotOwner(s)
 




eval
 - Evaluates code


restart
 - Restarts the bot's process


stop
 - Stops the bot's process

Update Logs


Logs on what has been added to this bot in all of it's updates is listed here.


The version number goes by 
Major
 > 
Moderate
 > 
Minor/Hotfix


Version 3.0.0


+ Added a command handler (discord.js-commando)


+ Recoded EVERYTHING!


+ Added jb!restart


+ Added jb!stop


+ Added jb!eval


- Removed jb!ate-guilds


- Removed jb!ate-restart


- Removed jb!ate-stop


- Removed jb!ate-eval


- Removed jb!ate-ping


- Removed jb!ate-check





Version 2.4.0


+ Added jb!apexianetwork


+ Added jb!sweatychildren


+ Hooked into the discordbots.group api


+ Hooked into the botlist.space api


+ Hooked into the discordboats.club api





Version 2.3.0


+ Added utilities module


+ Added jb!weather 


+ Added jb!vote


+ Added jb!list


+ Hooked into the listcord.com api





Version 2.2.3


+ Added jb!paidpromotion


+ Added jb!nose


+ Added jb!bloodyhell


+ Added a bot blacklist


+ Merged the donator file with the blacklist file (perms.json file)


+ Modified the symbol in the bot for memes





Version 2.2.2


+ Added jb!partner


+ Added jb!sweatychildren (alias of `jb!partner`)


+ Added jb!sc (alias of `jb!partner`)


+ Made the bot restart every hour (since then uptime has been great)





Version 2.2.1


+ Added jb!monster


+ Added jb!duet


+ Added jb!broke

+ Created the module videomemes
